ygData.subject: Re: [eqbards] Digest Number 836
ygData.msgSnippet: Over on CoN the question was raised of high level Mobs that people dream of killing was raised. Without hesitation I of course said all Brownies on Quellious
ygData.messageBody:
Over on CoN the question was raised of high level Mobs that people dream of
killing was raised. Without hesitation I of course said all Brownies on
Quellious' Green Norrath. Dead, dead dead. Then run through with pins and
stuck to every tree in Lesser Faydark as a festive decoration. *twitch*"

*regains composure*

However, number two was Dvinn:

Dvinn. But it's not about dying really, in two or three levels he shall be
my pet and he shall dance for me. He will take a tour of the castle killing
the Orcs with whom he conspires, then, after screenshots with him in
embarassing situations, I shall fear then chain him and kill him slowly with
sickly yellow DoTs.*twitch, blink blink*


Ummm...until what level will I have to wait to make this fantasy a reality?



Tszaaz E'Taurguin, Povar

P.S. Volenteer Renlor, the Walmart Greeter of Highpass was next. (Not that
he is high level, but I can't lose any more faction in Highpass) "No Renlor"
I shall tell him as he dies, "I do NOT want help with this gnoll".*twitch,
twitch, spasm*

-----

*Whips up a tea from Hill Giant Toes and Griff Feathers and hands it to
Tszaaz*

That should stop the twitching.

-Treehugger and Songmaker
Povar
